Bootstrap Phase-1
1.Create a container.
2.Input box to show the generated password
2.Label and inputbox for password length.
3.Label for (UPPERCASE) and checkbox.

-------Javascript (logic) phase1 upperCase letter--------

1. Input password length from user.


2.if length !='' AND Checkbox  checked;
    Generate random uppercase letter.
    else
    Generate a alertbox(Please enter the length and tick atleast one checkBox).

3. Display the Generated password in the inputBox.


-----Bootstrap Phase-2------

1.Create a new row.
2.And 2 columns one for the label and another for the checkbox.

-------Javascript (logic) phase-2 LowerCase letter------

1. Run a loop till the password length.
2. check if lowerCase is checked or not.
3. if checked than generate the lowerCase letter till password length.

-----Bootstrap Phase-3------

Repeat the phase-2 steps.

---------Javascript (logic) phase-3 for numbers-------

1. Created a random function to generate random number in a range (min, max).
2.Random function will generate number and select the random letter from the checked categories.
3. If number is checked than include numbers in the password and concatenate the string.
